{"tid":1724954,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗︰區選後展開次輪社區對話","createTime":"2019-11-15T15:16:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T14:01:04.000Z","uid":4281,"like":2,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"25fc572e995134f8e62e3e148472a52867f20b57","tid":1724954,"uid":4281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:16:53.000Z","msg":"張建宗:區選後展開次輪社區對話<br />\n<br />\n署理行政長官張建宗出席行政會議前說，第二輪社區對話，將於本月下旬區議會選舉後展開，又指討論內容會較上次對話詳細。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗表示，政府一直有與不同人士進行閉門深度對話，而閉門的原因，是希望保障人士身份，他又強調司局長亦會落區與市民接觸，以「三管齊下」方式與市民交流。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aeb6d9b0479b9e34eccc4a22daf4d98e49693f2","tid":1724954,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:17:24.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n韓國戰線要人呀！！完全冇人簽<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8f0046b8aabdfd4626486df60e834c63e0828dcb","tid":1724954,"uid":15730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:18:06.000Z","msg":"光頭佬收皮"},{"pid":"7e95f899aeb37dea2bdd78f65165679c1ecefa5d","tid":1724954,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:18:24.000Z","msg":"其實冇人想去"},{"pid":"6a8a111c1c1d97b582cb1b5014c3b56dc133271a","tid":1724954,"uid":289021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:19:10.000Z","msg":"傾完就出老解"},{"pid":"14ea27adf8c0cde2f9fe4ee285d7f52a33f9fcf3","tid":1724954,"uid":252877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:19:26.000Z","msg":"食屎啦，個政府都唔理民意，仲傾黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3957a08263ebe4373c367ec26e3ee74cc1b8f3","tid":1724954,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:19:28.000Z","msg":"夠膽唔帶保鏢唔帶差佬開路自己行入去大型屋邨搵人同你傾計之後安全返出嚟我支持你做特首又點話"},{"pid":"cb55c107e9fac0517efd4b6fcf6a